data.description: Embrace the allure of waterfront living in this exquisite three-bedroom, three-bathroom gem constructed in 2022. Revel in the upgraded white kitchen, showcasing sleek stainless-steel Whirlpool appliances, wood cabinets crowned with molding, a spacious island with quartz counters, and a convenient pantry.This townhome's charm extends through the main living area, adorned with Plantation Shutters and vinyl flooring. The master suite beckons with a walk-in closet and picturesque views of the serene lake. Experience modern convenience with upgrades like a programmable thermostat and a Wi-Fi-enabled garage door opener.
